      summary:
        'If you want to add more <b>American</b> recipes to your collection, Halloween Mocha Cupcakes might be a recipe you should try. One serving contains <b>382 calories</b>, <b>6g of protein</b>, and <b>22g of fat</b>. This recipe serves 12 and costs $1.39 per serving. It will be a hit at your <b>Halloween</b> event. A mixture of baking powder, sugar, bittersweet chocolate chips, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so tasty. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes approximately <b>45 minutes</b>. A couple people made this recipe, and 10 would say it hit the spot. It is brought to you by Foodista. It works well as a dessert. Overall, this recipe earns a <b>rather bad spoonacular score of 24%</b>. Users who liked this recipe also liked <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/halloween-cupcakes-1087715">Halloween cupcakes</a>, <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/halloween-cupcakes-63459">Halloween Cupcakes</a>, and <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/halloween-cupcakes-277474">Halloween Cupcakes</a>.',
      cuisines: ["American"],
